body:
It possible to move single point inside skPath without recreate it?

```
      public void OffsetPointAt(int index, SKPoint p)
        {
            var points = skPath.Points;
            points[index] += p;
            CreatePath(points);
            IsDirty = true;
        }

        protected virtual void CreatePath(SKPoint[] points)
        {
            skPath.Reset();
            skPath.AddPoly(points, true);
        }
```
OffsetPointAt called from touch handler, on move.
